title: Samsung Galaxy Buds
description: Upgrade your sound and style with Samsung Galaxy Buds Live. Designed with the largest Galaxy Buds speaker, improved bass and an open fit, playlists sound more like live music than ever before. When you need to block out background noise for a phone call or important task, initiate Active Noise Cancellation* with a touch. Buds Live are easy on the eyes, light on the ears and have long-lasting battery life.

title: Skullcandy Dime XT 2
description: Dime XT 2 in black is Skullcandy's smallest, lightest earbud ever and it has been updated to include Personal Sound. Skullcandy's premium audio quality delivers the kind of full, rich listening experience usually found in much more expensive earbuds. Dual microphones allow you to use either earbud solo even when you're taking a call. It is also has a noise isolating fit and is sweat and water-resistant, so it will stand up to workouts and outdoor adventures and you can listen without worry since it's backed by Tile Finding Technology.

title: TOZO T12 True
description: The T12 wireless earbuds use advanced Bluetooth 5.0 technology, which can easily enter the Bluetooth settings of the mobile phone to pair the headset in one step, provide stereo sound during calls, and also have fast and stable transmission. The in-ear headphones feature touch control sensors that minimize stress on your ears when you touch buttons for various functions. The nano-coating inside the earbuds and charging case is water-resistant to 1 meter for 30 minutes, suitable for sports and fitness.
